{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"7":"Fasting"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1706,"arabicnumber":1706,"text":"It was narrated from ‘Abdullah bin ‘Amr that the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said:“There is no fasting for one who fasts continually.”","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Hasan Or Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":7,"hadith":69}}]}